- constitution.md ⟨n principles⟩ / target ≤ 9
- oversized files ⟨…⟩

## Design doc score (sampled)
⟨per-dimension pass rate⟩

## Reference & drift
- Dangling references: ⟨n⟩
- Knowledge ↔ code drift: ⟨n⟩

